		<title>Nick Cao: Make A Killing In Retail Properties In China&#8217;s Tier-Two Cities</title>
		<link>http://www.chinamoneypodcast.com/2012/06/05/nick-cao-make-a-killing-in-retail-properties-in-chinas-tier-two-cities/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nick-cao-make-a-killing-in-retail-properties-in-chinas-tier-two-cities</link>
