		<title>Ludvig Nilsson: China&#8217;s Western Regions Are Private Equity&#8217;s Golden Frontier</title>
		<link>http://www.chinamoneypodcast.com/2012/05/30/ludvig-nilsson-chinas-western-regions-are-private-equitys-golden-frontier/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ludvig-nilsson-chinas-western-regions-are-private-equitys-golden-frontier</link>
